"nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fifty-fiftys-keena-drops-lawsuit-against-attrakt-returns-to-label-3516206">《五十五十》之后的 Keena 撤销了对 Attrakt 的诉讼，回归厂牌，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥要求马丁·斯科塞斯在《花月杀手》剧本写作两年后进行彻底修改https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese-overhaul-killers-of-the-flower-moon-script-3516208?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=leonardo-dicaprio-martin-斯科塞斯大修花月杀手剧本Surej SinghTue, 17 Oct 2023 04:54:33 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3516208 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这个故事的核心在哪里？”</p><p>莱昂纳多<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese-overhaul-killers-of-the-flower-moon-script-3516208">·迪卡普里奥 (Leonardo DiCaprio) 要求马丁·斯科塞斯 (Martin Scorsese) 在创作两年后彻底修改《花月杀手》剧本的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>电影制片人透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/martin-scorsese">马丁·斯科塞斯</a>在为<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/killers-of-the-flower-moon"><em>《花月杀手》</em></a>撰写剧本两年后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leonardo-dicaprio">莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥</a>要求进行大修。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">《花月杀手》评论：马丁·斯科塞斯令人心碎的真实犯罪冷门</a></strong></li></ul><p>斯科塞斯在接受<a href="https://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/2023/10/14/martin-scorsese-one-has-to-take-chances-at-this-age-what-else-can-i-do/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《爱尔兰时报》</em></a>采访时透露，他已经为这部即将上映的真实犯罪电影的剧本工作了两年，当莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥读到剧本并要求重新创作时。</p><p> <em>《花月杀手》改编</em>自 20 年代俄克拉荷马州奥塞奇部落的一系列谋杀案，由莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥、罗伯特·德尼罗、杰西·普莱蒙、莉莉·格拉德斯通和布兰登·费舍主演。</p><p>虽然这部电影现在是从奥塞奇部落的角度讲述的，但情况并非总是如此。根据斯科塞斯的说法，电影的原始剧本是“从前来调查的局特工的角度讲述的”，这引发了迪卡普里奥对剧本的质疑。</p><p>斯科塞斯解释道：“里奥来找我，问我，‘这个故事的核心在哪里？’我曾与奥色治人开会并共进晚餐，我想，好吧，故事就是这样。我们认为，真正的故事不一定来自局外，而是来自俄克拉荷马州内部。” </p><figure id="attachment_3425227" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3425227" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3425227" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon.jpeg" alt="莉莉·格莱斯顿和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥在《花月杀手》中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/DiCaprio-Killers-Flower-Moon-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3425227" class="wp-caption-text">莉莉·格莱斯顿和莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥在《花月杀手》中（图片来源：Apple）</figcaption></figure><p>为此，电影制片人会见了俄克拉荷马州灰马社区的 300 名成员。 “我总是说，如果我参与任何与土著人民有关的事情，我最好知道他们是谁，或者至少对他们作为人类感到满意，”斯科塞斯告诉《<em>爱尔兰时报》</em> 。</p><p>五月，当这部电影在戛纳首映时，奥塞奇族的主要酋长杰弗里·站立熊谈到这部电影和斯科塞斯时说：“马蒂·斯科塞斯代表奥塞奇族恢复了信任。我们知道信任不会被背叛。”</p><p> <em>《花月杀手》</em>计划于 10 月在全球影院上映，最终登陆 Apple TV+。</p><p>今年早些时候， <em>《NME》</em>成功抢先放映了这部电影，卢·托马斯 (Lou Thomas) 给予了这部电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">五星级的好评</a>。托马斯写道：“这是斯科塞斯最重要的作品之一。 1920 年代的流行音乐、美洲原住民歌曲和罗比·罗伯逊的蓝调音乐使这部非凡的西部片更加完美，这部电影将在观众的脑海中萦绕很长一段时间。”</p><p>莱昂纳多<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leonardo-dicaprio-martin-scorsese-overhaul-killers-of-the-flower-moon-script-3516208">·迪卡普里奥 (Leonardo DiCaprio) 要求马丁·斯科塞斯 (Martin Scorsese) 在创作两年后彻底修改《花月杀手》剧本的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
